<$TOP/mkfiles/mkfile.proto

CC=8c
# -H2 = H_PLAN9: force Plan 9 a.out for every 386 binary (kernel and
# userland). goken's 8l now defaults its header to ELF on a Linux host
# (via getgoos()), but all of principia must stay Plan 9 a.out. Baking the
# flag into $LD covers the kernel too, whose mkfile calls $LD without
# $LDFLAGS. (5l/vl still default to Plan 9, so arm/mips need no such flag.)
LD=8l -H2
O=8
AS=8a
